二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required Texts教師自編講義與教材
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online Resources


三、教學目標 Objectives


1.	將導遊領隊產業的現況介紹給同學2.	使其暸解並體驗導遊、領隊實務工作內容3.	培養學生國際禮儀、口語表達、臨場反應與應對進退等技巧4.	輔導考取專業證照，以提升職場競爭力 


1.	To introduce students with the current situation of the Taiwan tourism industry.2.	To familiarize students with the work-related content and context of tour guide and tour manager3.	To cultivate among students international etiquette, oral expression and situational response4.	To help students obtain a professional license. 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall Description介紹導遊領隊相關專業知識，包括導遊實務、領隊實務、航空票務、觀光資源概要與法規、觀光英語、國際禮儀、緊急事件處理等。並且將包含五場校外專家演講。期末考將以證照考試模擬考試方式舉行。The course contents include tour guide/manager practices, ticketing, sight-seeing resources and regulations, English for tourism, international etiquette and emergency management. Five talks will be given by outside experts. The final exam will be conducted in the form of a practice exam for the official license.

